metadata.name: Honey, are you asleep?
metadata.description:
Married a beautiful wife, the wedding night but can not touch, can not touch, even the bed can not, can only hold the knee against the wall in the corner......



Xiao Che really felt the malice of the world.



Red candle slightly drag, reflect a ambiguous bridal chamber. The room suddenly fell into a long silence, two people are dressed in red, a cold and proud quiet sitting on the bed, a poor shrinking in the corner, can only vaguely hear their own breathing.



After a long time, Xiao Che finally could not help but say: "You will not... Do you really want me to spend the night here?"
